      "behavior": "For create_project: validate owner exists in members, generate new project_id, set status to 'planning', record creation time, add to projects data store, return success. For update_project: check project exists, update provided fields (description, owner, status, deadline), validate owner if provided, return success. For delete_project: check project exists, delete all tasks associated with the project (if a task is assigned, release the member by setting availability to 'available'), remove project from data store, return success. All operations handle errors with appropriate messages.",
